{"type": "article", "id": 23383, "title": "可擦的“瓶子”", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-07T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115123TZFWyaBIQb3GRXtr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">手机、平板和电脑的屏幕都需要清洗维护，但想必很少有人会使用专用的清洁剂和抹布这样的搭配吧。立陶宛设计师 Julius Bučelis 就将它们合二为一设计了这个小工具，正方形的布料里装上清洁液体，相当于瓶身，其中一个角削掉安装了喷雾头，在喷洒液体之后就可以马上擦拭了。扁平的“瓶身”相较于圆形瓶身也更容易装在包里。这个设计获得了 2015 年 IF 奖，<a href=\"http://bucelis.com/#drop\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115121PlQhiFebMfxH8k3y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115121TdJP5REmfOeaZ4hc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115122502A3HR7Gitscz9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115122IWlTy3jDC69Rg75J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}